== 颁授 ==
新西兰维多利亚十字勋章旨在奖励{{cquote|“……最勇敢、或是最卓越的勇士，或是勇于自我牺牲者，或是面对敌人仍能彻底忠于职守的人。”<ref name="Govrefpack">{{cite web | url = http://img.scoop.co.nz/media/pdfs/0707/VCmediakit2jul07.pdf | format = PDF | title = Press kit related to july 2007 gallantry awards (NZ) | publisher = NZ Government through news agency | accessdate = 2013-11-17 | archivedate = 2012-02-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120205182318/http://img.scoop.co.nz/media/pdfs/0707/VCmediakit2jul07.pdf | deadurl = no}}</ref>}}

正式授予新西兰维多利亚勋章的权力属于[[新西兰君主|新西兰女王]]。皇家认证上称：“新西兰英勇勋章只能在我们新西兰总理的推荐下，或是由我们代理总理职位的内阁阁员推荐下，由我们，或是我们的后嗣和继任者授予。”<ref name="Warrant">{{cite web |url=http://medals.nzdf.mil.nz/warrants/d1nzgb-warrant.html |title=Royal Warrant |deadurl=no |publisher=NZDF | accessdate=2013-11-17 |quote=Awards of a New Zealand Gallantry Award and of a Bar to an Award shall be made by Us, Our Heirs and Successors, only on a recommendation by Our Prime Minister of New Zealand or a Minister of the Crown acting for Our Prime Minister. |archivedate=2012-02-05 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120205205907/http://medals.nzdf.mil.nz/warrants/d1nzgb-warrant.html}}</ref>而原来的维多利亚十字勋章则是由[[新西兰国防军|新西兰国防军]]到新西兰国防部的指挥链来提出授奖建议<ref name="Govrefpack" />。

英国的维多利亚十字勋章先后授予给过24位新西兰人，其中13枚是针对[[第一次世界大战|第一次世界大战]]期间的英勇行为。新西兰的维多利亚十字勋章自设立以来还只授予过一次，于2007年7月2日正式宣布<ref name="fullcitation">{{cite web|url=http://www.army.mil.nz/downloads/pdf/media-kit/20070702/citations.pdf |format=PDF |title=Full citation for Bill Apiata |publisher=NZDF |date=2007-07-02 |accessdate=2007-08-02 |archivedate=2007-09-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927222259/http://www.army.mil.nz/downloads/pdf/media-kit/20070702/citations.pdf }}</ref>。获得者是新西兰空军特种部队的威利·阿皮雅塔下士，他于2004年在[[阿富汗战争_(2001年)|阿富汗]]的一次冲击中“冒着敌军猛烈的火力挽救了战友的生命”<ref name="Govrefpack" /><ref name="PressRelease">{{cite web | archivedate = 2013-03-18 | url = http://www.scoop.co.nz/stories/PA0707/S00013.htm | title = Gallantry in Afghanistan | publisher = NZ Government through news agency | accessdate = 2013-11-17 |deadurl=no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130318184202/http://www.scoop.co.nz/stories/PA0707/S00013.htm}}</ref>。阿皮雅塔于2007年7月26日在惠林顿总督府举办的一场仪式上从新西兰总督[[阿南德·萨蒂亚南德|阿南德·萨蒂亚南德]]手中接過这枚勋章<ref name="VCreceived">{{cite news | url = http://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/news/article.cfm?c_id=1&objectid=10453961 | title = Willie Apiata receives his VC | work = The New Zealand Herald | date = 2007-07-26 | accessdate = 2013-11-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130928234255/http://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/news/article.cfm?c_id=1&objectid=10453961 | archive-date = 2013-09-28 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

